{"tid":1478703,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（急）有關聽日紅土嘅注意事項","createTime":"2019-08-16T15:29:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T15:52:27.000Z","uid":255628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"85ce629586def3f2e72f20880436ea687074ceed","tid":1478703,"uid":255628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:29:58.000Z","msg":"小弟身為地道黃埔人 <br />\n自然期待左期待紅土遊行好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假若聽日真係搞得成嘅話<br />\n咁諗住聽日去嘅咁多位巴絲聽住<br />\n千祈千祈要記得<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">遊行係將會以非法嘅本質黎進行</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">所以各位就算打算淨係去遊完行就走嘅都要帶定少少gear!!! 因為無人估到啲夠會唔會隨時清場或者採取其他行動黎驅散</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">各位手足可帶定簡單保護到自身安全同以防識別到身分嘅gear : <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>1) 口罩</strong><br />\n<strong>2）勞工手套</strong><br />\n<strong>3）黑超/眼罩<br />\n[b]4） 帽</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後提醒大家<br />\n如果唔係要救人或者裝備充足低下嘅情況<br />\n盡量唔好同狗博<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">期待聽日所有紅土巴絲一齊出黎遊行</span>"},{"pid":"2c3fad78b229ffaf464dc61c901a13870c0cceb4","tid":1478703,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:30:27.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"05ea55765eb770f8485260a611e654e91dd1e330","tid":1478703,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:31:04.000Z","msg":"鬼先最想我